# - Find FMOD includes and library
#
# This module defines
#  FMOD_INCLUDE_DIRS
#  FMOD_LIBRARIES, the libraries to link against to use FMOD.
#  FMOD_LIBRARY_DIRS, the location of the libraries
#  FMOD_FOUND, If false, do not try to use FMOD
